+#### 6. **Natural Interaction Models**
+- **High Satisfaction:** Todoist (natural language), Alarmy (puzzle/photo), Sleep Cycle (passive sleep tracking)
+- **What Works:** Interface mirrors how humans think about task
+- **Why:** Reduces friction to regular use
+- **Implication:** Study your user's mental model; match the app to it
